裡有一些與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看（<a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php）。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk%2Fmyth_showlist.php%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82&d=YHOK1jkDVubwOHU1GrJP%2FeI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=28b18315\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php）。</a> 你更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"cd111ceb9850db9af749e7c84d865bf318553638","tid":887555,"uid":180734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98e9bd68bf94758c8024ae7c723313149e8d38be","tid":887555,"uid":1110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T06:19:43.000Z","msg":"我呢排都好空虛<br />\n鐘意既女仔對我無feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T06:48:42.000Z","msg":"i know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}